            "title": "盤中速報 - 信音(6126)大漲7.12%，報36.1元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>信音(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6126:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6126\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6126-TW</a>)16日12:44股價上漲2.4元，報36.1元，漲幅7.12%，成交7,131張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>信音(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6126:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6126\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6126-TW</a>)所屬產業為電子零組件業，主要業務為各種電子電腦及週邊設備之零件製造裝配及買賣。各種鋼模及金屬沖品之製造及買賣。塑膠玩具、電池玩具(電動玩具除外)之製造裝配及買賣。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌2.6%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.96%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-453 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-462 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+9 張</li> <li>融資增減：-58 張</li> <li>融券增減：-10 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6312960",
