            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "id": 6312952,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 昭輝(1339)大漲9.83%，報47.5元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>昭輝(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1339:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1339\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1339-TW</a>)16日12:31股價上漲4.25元，報47.5元，漲幅9.83%，成交263張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>昭輝(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1339:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1339\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1339-TW</a>)所屬產業為汽車工業，主要業務為汽車零組件之製造及銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲2.98%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲1.48%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-9 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-9 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：0 張</li> <li>融資增減：+51 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
